### Pipeline 示例

以 registeration 为例，在pipeline中通过 podTemplate 动态生成 jenkins 节点：
```bash
#!/usr/bin/env groovy

properties([
	buildDiscarder(
		logRotator(
		    artifactDaysToKeepStr: '',
		    artifactNumToKeepStr: '3',
		    daysToKeepStr: '',
		    numToKeepStr: '3'
		)
	)
])

podTemplate(
    containers: [
        containerTemplate(
            image: 'registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/smb/jnlp-slave', 
            name: 'jnlp', 
            ttyEnabled: true, 
            alwaysPullImage: true, 
            workingDir: '/home/jenkins'
        )
    ], 
    label: 'smb', 
    name: 'guiyu', 
    cloud: 'kubernetes', 
    namespace: 'kube-jenkins', 
    imagePullSecrets: [ 'guiji' ], 
    serviceAccount: 'jenkins', 
    volumes: [
        nfsVolume(mountPath: '/root/.m2', readOnly: false, serverAddress: '192.168.4.81', serverPath: '/home/data/nfs/maven_repository'),
        hostPathVolume(hostPath: '/var/run/docker.sock', mountPath: '/var/run/docker.sock'), 
        hostPathVolume(hostPath: '/home/data/nfs/.kube', mountPath: '/home/jenkins/.kube')
    ]) {
    node("smb"){

        stage("checkout"){
            checkout scm
        }

        def commitID = sh(returnStdout: true, script: "git rev-parse --short HEAD").trim()
        def moduleName = "registeration"
        def tag = commitID
        def workDir = "src/back/guiyu-parent/guiyu-cloud-parent/guiyu-cloud-registeration"
        
        dir(workDir){
            stage("maven package"){
                // withMaven (maven: 'mvn') {
                    sh "mvn -v"
                    sh "mvn clean package -Dmaven.test.skip=true"
                // }
            archiveArtifacts artifacts: 'target/*.jar', onlyIfSuccessful: true
            }
            stage("build image"){
                withDockerRegistry(credentialsId: '155a1f29-a0da-4955-8b71-49e82ea5e3c0', url: 'https://registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com') {
                sh "docker build -t registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/smb/${moduleName}:${tag} ."
                sh "docker push registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/smb/${moduleName}:${tag}"
                sh "docker rmi registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/smb/${moduleName}:${tag}"
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
```

### Jenkins slave镜像制作

以官方 jenkinsci/jnlp-slave 镜像为基础，制作我们需要的镜像。
Dockerfile:

```bash
FROM jenkinsci/jnlp-slave
MAINTAINER changbin<changbin@guiji.ai>

USER root
# timezone
RUN apt-get update && \
 apt-get install -y tzdata && \
 ln -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime && \
 echo "Asia/Shanghai" > /etc/timezone

# install maven
RUN apt-get install curl tar bash
ARG MAVEN_VERSION=3.3.9
ARG USER_HOME_DIR="/home/jenkins"
RUN mkdir -p /usr/share/maven /usr/share/maven/ref \
 && curl -fsSL http://apache.osuosl.org/maven/maven-3/$MAVEN_VERSION/binaries/apache-maven-$MAVEN_VERSION-bin.tar.gz \
 | tar -xzC /usr/share/maven --strip-components=1 \
 && ln -s /usr/share/maven/bin/mvn /usr/bin/mvn
ENV MAVEN_HOME /usr/share/maven
ENV MAVEN_CONFIG "$USER_HOME_DIR/.m2"

# Install Docker client
ENV DOCKER_BUCKET download.docker.com
ENV DOCKER_VERSION 19.03.8
RUN set -x \
 && curl -fSL "https://${DOCKER_BUCKET}/linux/static/stable/x86_64/docker-$DOCKER_VERSION.tgz" -o docker.tgz \
 && tar -xzvf docker.tgz \
 && mv docker/* /usr/local/bin/ \
 && rmdir docker \
 && rm docker.tgz \
 && docker -v

#kubectl
COPY kubectl ./kubectl
RUN chmod +x kubectl \
 && mv ./kubectl /usr/local/bin/kubectl
```
